{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0003", "text": "我錯什麼 狠狠的棄於 漆黑的角落", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 2, 3, 9, 9, 3, 4, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "co3", "sam6", "mo1", "han2", "han2", "dik1", "hei3", "jyu1", "cat1", "hak1", "dik1", "gok3", "lok6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我錯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "狠狠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "棄於", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "漆黑", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "角落", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0004", "text": "大雨裏滂沱 找不到我地方", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 5, 0, 0, 9, 3, 4, 5, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daai6", "jyu5", "leoi5", "pong4", "to4", "zaau2", "bat1", "dou3", "ngo5", "dei6", "fong1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "大雨", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "裏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "滂沱", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "地方", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0005", "text": "如他更好 想你可 真的泊岸", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 9, 9, 5, 9, 3, 3, 2, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "taa1", "hou2", "soeng2", "nei5", "ho2", "zan1", "dik1", "bok6", "ngon6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "更好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "真的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "泊岸", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0006", "text": "如他更好 便忘掉 殘落花朵", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 9, 2, 0, 2, 0, 2, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "taa1", "hou2", "bin6", "mong4", "diu6", "caan4", "lok6", "faa1", "do2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "更好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "便", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "忘掉", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "殘落", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "花朵", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0007", "text": "我有什麼 應該怎去撐 一生的跌蕩", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 2, 3, 3, 9, 4, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "jau5", "sam6", "mo1", "goi1", "zam2", "heoi3", "caang1", "jat1", "sang1", "dik1", "dit3", "dong6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "應該", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "撐", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一生", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跌蕩", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0008", "text": "沒有你陪航 看天茫茫 沒感覺地流浪", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 5, 0, 0, 4, 3, 0, 0, 2, 9, 4, 2, 0, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mut6", "jau5", "nei5", "pui4", "hong4", "hon3", "tin1", "mong4", "mong4", "mut6", "gam2", "gok3", "dei6", "lau4", "long6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "陪航", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "看天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "茫茫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "感覺", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "地", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "流浪", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0009", "text": "曾講過地球沒星光 都跟我白頭和天荒", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 4, 2, 0, 2, 3, 3, 3, 3, 5, 2, 0, 0, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cang4", "gong2", "gwo3", "dei6", "kau4", "mut6", "sing1", "gwong1", "dou1", "gan1", "ngo5", "baak6", "tau4", "wo4", "tin1", "fong1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "曾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "講", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "地球", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "星光", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "白頭", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "和", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天荒", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0010", "text": "然而現在誰伴你過 他不是我", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 2, 0, 2, 5, 4, 3, 3, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jin4", "ji4", "jin6", "zoi6", "seoi4", "bun6", "nei5", "gwo3", "taa1", "bat1", "si6", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "然而", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "現在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "伴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0011", "text": "溫馨片段太過清楚 跟你一切誰又敢忘", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 9, 2, 4, 4, 3, 9, 3, 5, 3, 4, 0, 2, 9, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["wan1", "hing1", "pin2", "dyun6", "taai3", "gwo3", "cing1", "co2", "gan1", "nei5", "jat1", "cai3", "seoi4", "jau6", "gam2", "mong4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "溫馨", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "片段", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "清楚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一切", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "敢", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "忘", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0012", "text": "誰知到這天 竟隔了銀河", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 4, 5, 3, 9, 4, 5, 0, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "zi1", "dou3", "ze5", "tin1", "ging2", "gaak3", "liu5", "ngan4", "ho4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "竟隔", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "銀河", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0013", "text": "回憶裏是甜蜜的歌 今天再聽仍能聽麼", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 5, 2, 0, 2, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 3, 0, 0, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["wui4", "jik1", "leoi5", "si6", "tim4", "mat6", "dik1", "go1", "gam1", "tin1", "zoi3", "ting1", "jing4", "nang4", "ting1", "mo1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "回憶", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "裏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "甜蜜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "歌", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "今天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "聽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "聽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "麼", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0014", "text": "誰曾話沒人代替我 他不是我", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 2, 0, 2, 4, 5, 3, 3, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "cang4", "waa6", "mut6", "jan4", "doi6", "tai3", "ngo5", "taa1", "bat1", "si6", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "曾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "話", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "代替", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "星光", "artists": ["鄭俊弘"], "lyricists": ["楊熙"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6446", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR5L-K5byY_NjQ0Ng_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
